snippet.title: Who got attacked on social media | The Lexicon Ep. 3
snippet.description:
This week's video covers my thoughts on Justin Bieber's latest Instagram scandals, Amber Heard and Johnny Depp's settlement and Ellen's meme that caused an uproar. As always, I am sharing my thoughts in this video. I hope it didn't offend you! 

Justin Bieber is being attacked on Instagram:
http://www.vanityfair.com/style/2016/08/justin-bieber-nude-photo-chantal-jeffries?mbid=social_facebook
http://www.eonline.com/news/787861/selena-gomez-backtracks-on-social-media-comments-while-justin-bieber-deletes-his-instagram

Amber Heard and Johnny Depp come to an agreement:
http://www.eonline.com/news/788633/amber-heard-donating-entire-7-million-divorce-settlement-to-charities-to-help-those-less-able-to-defend-themselves

Ellen DeGeneres is NOT racist: 
http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-3743786/Ellen-DeGeneres-accused-racist-posting-Usain-Bolt-meme-showed-riding-back.html
http://abcnews.go.com/Entertainment/ellen-degeneres-responds-accusations-usain-bolt-tweet-racist/story?id=41453105
